#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.61"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.61:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.61:0.2"
msgid "6. Upayavagga "
msgstr "6. Involvement "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.61:0.3"
msgid "61. Ādittasutta "
msgstr "61. Burning "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.61:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.61:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, ādittaṃ, vedanā ādittā, saññā ādittā, saṅkhārā ādittā, viññāṇaṃ ādittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are burning. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.61:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi … saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.61:1.4"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.61:1.5"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.61:1.6"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
